name: ArTime
description: "Introducing our exclusive Watch NFT Collection, where time meets artistry! Each NFT features a one-of-a-kind, intricately designed watch face, blending futuristic aesthetics with timeless elegance. These digital timepieces are more than just art—they’re a statement of individuality and innovation. Own a piece of the future, where every tick is a masterpiece. Limited edition, uniquely yours."

name: Breaking Free
description:
NFT Collection: "Breaking Free – A Journey to Strength"

A powerful and emotional NFT series that symbolizes the journey of breaking free from a narcissistic relationship and embracing inner strength, self-healing, and transformation. Each piece in this exclusive collection captures a profound moment of liberation, resilience, and rebirth, resonating with those who have overcome toxic cycles and emerged stronger.

name: Only Men Club
description:
ONLYMENCLUB (OMC) is an elite collection of 10,000 meticulously designed NFTs, embodying the diverse styles, preferences, and origins of the modern gentleman. Each handcrafted piece is a symbol of distinction and purpose.

OMC NFT holders gain exclusive access to The CLUB, a private space where men, creators, and entrepreneurs connect to discuss projects, entrepreneurship, business, and Web3 networking. Membership unlocks exclusive drops, real-world experiences, and a thriving community driven by ambition, collaboration, wealth, and success.

name: Pearling Expedition
description: A rare collection of historical photographs capturing the rich heritage of the Middle East. From the Land of Pearls to the vast Arabian Desert, each image tells a timeless story. Own a piece of history with our limited-edition digital archives, exclusively on OpenSea.”

name: Kawaii Girl 3D Figure
description:
I create adorable 3D CG illustrations of figurines.
Each piece I sell is one of a kind, making it truly unique in the world. 😊

name: The Emoji Project
description:
These NFTs are part of The Emoji Project—a set of uniquely designed, Web3-native emoji expressions that go beyond traditional emojis. Inspired by the open-source creativity of OpenMoji, this collection builds upon and reimagines digital expression for the decentralized era. 

Each NFT is a fully unique, collectible reaction icon that represents a mood, meme, or moment in the metaverse.Whether used as a collectible, a digital identity marker, or a piece of art, this NFT represents a new way to express yourself in Web3—bridging the past, present, and future of emoji culture.
